 "description": "Mermen swim 15\", 10% per 10 of grappling a ship within 1\" (surfaced to do it; submerged their moves are written; surfaced they draw missile fire); each grapple slows a ship 2\". Nixies (fresh water, 9\") need 40 for a grappling attempt. The Dragon Turtle — most fearsome of the waters — lifts ships on its back, moves 9\" (3\" ashore), breathes steam as a Red Dragon's fire, HD 11-13, otherwise a flightless dragon. Water Elementals stop ships and overturn small ones; Giant Leeches, Snakes, Octopi, Squids, Crabs, and Fish per their entries; and if the monsters don't get a ship, perhaps it will sail off the edge of the world!",
